WEBVTT

00:02.500 --> 00:03.750
Are you into skiing?

00:04.050 --> 00:06.100
Is winter your favorite time of year?

00:06.450 --> 00:08.350
If you like snow and ice,...

00:08.600 --> 00:12.450
...maybe you should stay at the Ice Hotel in Quebec, Canada.

00:13.050 --> 00:16.600
But you can only check in to this hotel during the winter.

00:17.050 --> 00:21.650
Why? Because this hotel is made entirely of ice and snow!

00:22.250 --> 00:25.200
This amazing hotel is built every December.

00:25.600 --> 00:30.300
It has 32 rooms and 80 people can stay there each night.

00:30.950 --> 00:35.350
The hotel has a movie theater, an art gallery, and a church.

00:35.850 --> 00:40.000
Of course, all of these parts of the hotel are made of ice.

00:40.400 --> 00:42.800
In fact, all the furniture, art,...

00:43.150 --> 00:47.750
...lights, and even plates, and drinking glasses are made of ice.

00:48.350 --> 00:52.700
Because this hotel is so unusual, it has become very popular.

00:53.100 --> 00:56.450
People from all over the world come to the Ice Hotel...

00:56.700 --> 00:59.050
...to look at the fantastic ice art,...

00:59.400 --> 01:02.050
...drink and eat from designer ice dishes,...

01:02.300 --> 01:04.600
...and experience the unique atmosphere.

01:05.200 --> 01:09.350
Some couples have even gotten married in the hotel's ice church.

01:10.000 --> 01:13.250
However, all the guests keep their winter coats on!

01:13.650 --> 01:14.950
Because of all the ice,...

01:15.200 --> 01:21.850
...the temperature inside the hotel is always between -2 and -5 degrees Celsius.

01:22.350 --> 01:27.300
Surprisingly, sleeping is not a problem in the freezing cold hotel rooms.

